item.title: CLASSIC LINE
item.content: <p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The culture and search for quality have created a fascinating and at the same time elegant product. The hides are of leather, the soles of natural or treated leather. Our mission is to build comfortable shoes, which apart from the design could be also comfortable during the whole day. We have different quality models. The search for details and design has created the most elegant shoe of our classic line.</p>
